  "elapsed_s": 11.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I joined that group, and had some interesting-- I would say, at that time, horrifying experiences-- which made me to leave that council to have a month or so.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Eichmann, who arrived to Budapest, demanded from the Judenrat [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] payment of-- and I don't remember the exact amount-- payment of a large sum of American dollars and a large amount of gold.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the Judenrat sent me with the letter, since I was the runner of the Judenrat, sent me with the letter that they only have half of what he wanted.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he went into a temper tantrum that it was very frightening, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] wrote a letter back, and also stated that he will arrest the whole council if they don't get the whole amount that he wanted.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So my next return with the letter that they have the whole amount was the last thing that I did for them, because he became even more angry, and I was afraid that he's going to become even more angry or do something.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But he didn't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He just sent me-- gave me another letter, and I don't know what was in there, because after that I resigned from that position and went to work in a brick factory.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I worked there until the middle of June.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] The invasion was on June the 6th.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I was still working in the factory, but shortly thereafter, there were movements-- military movements in our area-- which we could not explain why.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Later, we learned that Hungarian fascists mobilized approximately 40,000 gendarme to force the deportation of the Jews from Budapest.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "By that time, all the other Jews were deported, but Governor [?",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
